# Frank's Children

One day old Frank went to the pub for a pint. At the end of the night, Frank went home with a beautiful woman. Her name was Lilith. Frank and Lilith spent the night together. It was one hell of a night full of passion and fighting. The next morning, Lilith was gone because she only makes one night stands. She was also the manager of a hotel called Pandemonium and she had to go to work. But Lilith and Frank were connected now because Lilith was pregnant with twins.

Frank has two daughters:

- Aria
- Loulla

## Hobbies:

In their free time, Aria and Loulla like to go on long walks in the city. They are usually free after midnight. During the day, they clean the house and cook meals for Frank with the stuff they found during last night's walk.
